PositiveWidth: Scale the region in the POSITIVE width direction. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
NegativeWidth: Scale the region in the NEGATIVE width direction. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
PositiveHeight: Scale the region in the POSITIVE height direction. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
NegativeHeight: Scale the region in the NEGATIVE height direction. Range is 0-1. Default is 1.0.
